        <div class="card-block">
          <div class="card-text"><a href="https://help.github.com/enterprise/2.4/admin/guides/user-management/creating-teams/" target="_blank">Teams</a> give organizations the ability to create groups of members and control access to repositories. Team members can be granted read, write, or admin permissions to specific repositories. To create a team: </div></br>
          <ul class="card-text">
            <li>click your profile photo > 'Your profile'</li>
            <li>Organizations, click your org icon</li>
            <li>click 'Teams' under your org</li>
            <li>click 'New team'</li>
            <li>decide if it will be 'Visible'</li>
            <li>click 'Create team'</li>
